Add Cluster Variable in Grafana
Suggest the on-prem team add a cluster dropdown variable to their dashboards:
Dashboard Settings → Variables → New

Name    : cluster
Type    : Query
Query   : label_values(cluster)
Multi   : ON ✅
All     : ON ✅
Then use {cluster=~"$cluster"} in all panels — users can switch between clusters or view all at once with a single dropdown.